{"tid":2360645,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［文革模式］NY Time: 停止‘綏靖政策‘ 侵侵既盟友夥伴有參與犯罪行為嗎 佢哋必須’交代‘","createTime":"2021-01-10T03:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T05:58:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57597e115188b24c6505a8f9e00b8c5440b61c22","tid":2360645,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjmFUAr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjmFUAr.png&h=3518df22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n篇文結尾：<br />\n<br />\n那麼我們能做些什麼呢？是時候停止姑息我們當中的法西斯分子了。執法部門應該盡量設法逮捕週三襲擊事件的參與者&mdash;&mdash;其中一些人已經被確認，而且有視頻證據，可以很容易地確認更多人。<br />\n<br />\n任何試圖暴力干涉權力移交的人也應該被逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n最後，有必要對過去四年中發生的任何犯罪行為做個交代&mdash;&mdash;還有人懷疑特朗普的盟友和夥伴參與了犯罪行為嗎？不要說我們應該向前看而不是向後看；如果我們想讓未來變得更好，對過去的行為做出問責是至關重要的。<br />\n<br />\n綏靖政策讓我們走到了今天這一步。現在必須停止了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20210108/donald-trump-fascism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fopinion%2F20210108%2Fdonald-trump-fascism%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDRBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=17079139\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20210108/donald-trump-fascism/</a>"},{"pid":"4cdfb93daef97973183ddfb69a7cc663142b4f0d","tid":2360645,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"成個做法<br />\n污名name tag, 社評批鬥做勢<br />\n大公司打壓<br />\n完全係共產黨文革既手法"},{"pid":"1ed0ddce69fc6931be8510f810bd4a5318a39f49","tid":2360645,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90V7zBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90V7zBr.png&h=07b7e353&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pexaxn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPexaxn8.png&h=88ff7776&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a04ef7ba3b12bbfc609172cf58b97275